{
  "label": "Prestige",
  "costFormula": "power",
  "formulaNote": "cost = baseCost * pow(level, multCost) * breakpointMult * linearMult. level = new level being purchased (1-indexed). breakpointMult: x3 if level >= ceil(maxLevel*0.5), x8 additional if level >= ceil(maxLevel*0.8) (cumulative x24). linearMult: x(1 + level*0.001) if maxLevel > 999 and level > 1.",
